@UrlManagement.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5290

### Shorten URL
POST {{UrlManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/urls/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "originalUrl": "https://www.google.com"
}

### Get Original URL (Lookup)
GET {{UrlManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/api/urls/abc1234

### Redirect (Using root)
GET {{UrlManagement.Api_HostAddress}}/abc1234
